With Lollipop 5.0, Advanced Tools PRO made my external card writable using Titanium Pro. Superb app! Go to Settings of Advanced Tools PRO,  then enable root features followed by pressing SD Card write access.  Press Confirm button. In Titanium Backup Pro,  change Directory to /mnt/ExtSdCard/Titanium Backup. With these steps,  you will free more space in your Internal Card.
